h1. batch-reload-app

h2. Purpose

Reloads Grails application without killing the JVM that was previously started by a @batch-run-app@ command. 
It should be used from a different command line prompt.

h2. Example

{code}
grails batch-reload-app
{code}

h2. Description

Usage:
{code}
grails batch-reload-app
{code}

